<h2 id="interlude-riff">Interlude riff</h2>

<p>This is what you hear between each verse. Again, there are a few ways you can play it. Use the method(s) that work for your needs.</p>

<p>Variation A:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>e –––––––––––––––|––––––––––––|–––––––––––––––|––––––––––––
