D ––––––––7–7––––|–––––––5–5––|–––––––––––––––|––––––––––––
A ––7h8h9–––––9––|––5h7–––––––|––0h1h2––––––––|––––––––––––
E –––––––––––––––|––––––––––––|––––––––––––3––|––––––––––––
    D               C            G Variation B:

